Dear {!Primary_Applicant_Name__c},

Greetings from Runwal Enterprises!!

We are delighted to inform you that the possession and key handover formalities for your home have been successfully completed. Please find your unit details below for reference:

Project: {!Project__r.Name}
Tower/Wing: {!Tower__r.Name}
Unit Number: {!Unit_No__r.Name}
Possession Date: {!RW_Key_handover_date__c}

Congratulations on reaching this important milestone and becoming the proud owner of your new home. We sincerely thank you for your trust in Runwal Enterprises and for being a valued part of the Runwal family.

We wish you and your family many years of happiness, comfort, and wonderful memories in your new home.

For any post-possession assistance, please feel free to reach out to our customer support team.

Warm regards,
Runwal Enterprises
